HEADWORD: Missal
<hw>Mis"sal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>missale</ets>, liber <ets>missalis</ets>, from <ets>missa</ets>
mass: cf. F. <ets>missel</ets>. See 1st <er>Mass</er>.]</ety> <def>The
book containing the service of the Mass for the entire year; a Mass
book.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

