==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Missal
<hw>Mis"sal</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to the Mass, or to
a missal or Mass book.</def> <rj><au>Bp. Hall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
